features: [2 in 1 Glider Airplane Toy]: Combining 3 planes and a catapult pistol doubles the fun. Just pull the trigger and the plane will be launched quickly. It’s available to fly even if you use the plane alone, and the plane will fly out with a light throw. Simple and fun.

[Safe Material & Easy to Use]: The airplane is made of foam material, which is safe and non-toxic. It is light, the weight of a single airplane is only 25g. Just insert the wings into the fuselage and use it with the launcher gun, children can easily master its game play and have fun .

[Streamlined Design]: The airplane adopts a unique streamlined design and integrated counterweight to achieve the best center of gravity to enable the airplane to achieve the best flight conditions, improve the ability to glide in the air, and achieve rapid high-altitude flight.

[Fun Indoor Outdoor Sport Games]: By using this flying toy, children can exercise hand-eye coordination and relax their eyes. In the process of throwing and chasing the airplane, they can exercise and be happy. It is a fun and novel flying game.

[Interactive Educational Toy]: Children can play with their friends, which is conducive to exercise social skills. Parents can also join with kids and race to see who flies farther. Good for kids to learn knowledge about airplane and gravity from playing.
